’ђђЪTitle: title: 'This week in Nushell #331'
Path: Highlights
Content:
Polars hits the trifecta with AWS, Azure, and now, thanks to @ayax79 - Google Cloud Platform!
You can now both time a command and return its output using 
``timeit --output``
 thanks to @Tyarel8!
